,"uid":124292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:48:01.000Z","msg":"真係可恥至極"},{"pid":"4521f52fdce0d70e76a5eb9744875e38ceaea8d8","tid":1550681,"uid":16713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:48:37.000Z","msg":"將軍澳寶琳坑口同其他區拍埋一比真係高下立見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爭氣啲啦 人又係香港人 你地又係香港人"},{"pid":"93262b543501dee7fa85a846a28cebb31ed95025","tid":1550681,"uid":158889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"唔打狗 怕 可以接受 保護搞事藍絲 安全離場 不可接受"},{"pid":"8391fcf6eb5992def629fb1c0649c5a02a1bba41","tid":1550681,"uid":110331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:53:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">We may have lost a battle but NOT the war<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地今日機場喺輸左但場運動未</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日美領大遊行要齊人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要過左五大訴求就會成真！<br />\n政府要係2020實行真。普選立法會<br />\n侵犯人權的官員人和家庭成員簽證可被撤銷，外資可被凍結！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmfHUdC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmfHUdC.png&h=89bc45e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksEYsyD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FksEYsyD.png&h=ab62bc0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">呢個先喺真真正正嘅END GAME<br />\n未清楚咩事可以睇下面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">草案要求中國政府履行承諾，容許港人治港、高度自治，並且確保香港人可以通過普選，選出行政長官及立法會所有議席，當中特別設下「時限」，要求在2020年普選立法會。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2。</span></span></span><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">特別警告香港若就23條立法，除非可證明不影響港人及外籍居民的人權，否則美國政府可中止《香港政策法》等。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">3。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">侵犯人權的及損害香港自治的官員及人士的清單。名單裡的人在美國的資產可被凍結、個人和家庭成員的簽證可被撤銷，要求美國總統調查及制裁打壓香港自由的官員。會交代香港是否有官員因協助侵犯人權而需要受制裁。</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">這有助國際社會持續監察香港的狀況，如能每年通過查證，實際上等同美國年年為一國兩制投下信任一票，這一方面有助有助保障香港高度自治，同時亦會加強國際社會對香港的信心。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DYm9M6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DYm9M6.png&h=40ab8a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LehviFs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLehviFs.png&h=cadff255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">未簽聯署即做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=d94a9911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日12點遮打花園見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7A6LR0y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7A6LR0y.png&h=81aa1e4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"890122ed1e6d9ccbe688057f8196ffd86122637d","tid":1550681,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed625e21c1ab373379815d24af386472f3688b7","tid":1550681,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要說 「 左膠 」<br />\n<br />\n試着說 「 藍絲臥底 」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阻人嗰啲藍絲扮架，支持送中，支持警察架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:54:32.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔駛洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估19年先出現左膠咩<br />\n佢地慣常做法就係咁"},{"pid":"fcffafd53a08d5eccbba7a96bcf72c338f83f056","tid":1550681,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:07:59.000Z","msg":"將軍澳成班垃圾"},{"pid":"21758f589baaf7bfbe8317a2e2f82cdf9d725239","tid":1550681,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:19:40.000Z","msg":"最撚垃圾地區"},{"pid":"ff525b7f16e2623d50a5f2b83af43ee300c837f5","tid":1550681,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"我兩個POST上過熱門又點<br />\n都係得把口既多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e271f45869224ccc234b26e6ace78f8fa34d95","tid":1550681,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97f8d627f4456f8b2ae0ac180989dc631f47988a","tid":1550681,"uid":47905,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:56.000Z","msg":"放完藍絲<br />\n打左手足<br />\n<br />\n仲可以拍手叫加油<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm